This paper is related to database systems and query processing, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DB. Additionally, the use of MapReduce and GPU technologies indicates that it could also fit into categories such as cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.PF (Performance). Finally, the paper involves programming and implementation, which could place it in the cs.PL (Programming Languages) category.
